  "summaries": [
    {
      "id": "summary:contents",
      "type": "abstract",
      "value": "A compilation of three works: Piers Plowman represented by A, B, and C version streams; the anonymous political poem Richard the Redeless; and the anonymous The Crowned King. The source XML follows Skeat's EETS carriers and includes editorial apparatus but only the direct intellectual text is counted in extent.",
