    "description": "Exactly three intellectual works and 18,175 direct verse lines. Piers contributes A 2,580 + B 7,240 + C 7,354 = 17,174; Richard contributes 857; Crowned King 144. The raw XML has 18,184 L elements only because nine quotation lines are nested in NOTE1 (three in each Piers version). Raw A/B/C counts 2,583/7,243/7,357 are encoding metrics, not work extent.",
